{"tid":599255,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"西班牙稅局拒絕 C朗逃稅罰錢避坐監","createTime":"2018-03-20T08:46:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-22T11:16:18.000Z","uid":54373,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8e404f8f137e050210096f39e06fa95a97535aff","tid":599255,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T08:46:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">提出罰款已經係認罪一總?<br />\n何來光明正大?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2018年3月20日 上午6:12<br />\n基斯坦奴朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo）<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=ZhIX5m104SAY8N8dsYFrA%2BI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=782ec85e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】皇家馬德里球星基斯坦奴朗拿度涉嫌逃稅，據指早前<span style=\"color: red;\">向西班牙稅局提出繳交數百萬歐元罰款，以取代監禁刑罰，但遭當局拒絕</span>。<br />\n<br />\n西班牙檢察院去年6月正式向皇家馬德里球星前鋒基斯坦奴朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo）提出檢控，指這名葡萄牙球王從肖像權相關收入裡逃稅達1470萬歐元。據當地傳媒報道，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">C朗的代表律師曾經提出，承認犯錯</span></span>，並且向有關當局繳交罰款，以換取對方終止刑事檢控，亦能夠避過最高達3年半的牢獄之災。<br />\n<br />\n不過，據指經過面談後，C朗代表開價為大約400至500萬歐元，當局對此價碼非常不滿意，因而已經斷言拒絕。<br />\n<br />\nC朗去年夏天上庭<span style=\"color: red;\">作供時指，自己光明正大</span>，一向交足稅項，未來亦會繼續這樣做。"},{"pid":"649db06470f57c4a2a66b41c96661c1b96a8d5f9","tid":599255,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T09:13:00.000Z","msg":"屌 西甲又迫害我朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abb6898d4350f37b82d5ec539a56f93af451dea8","tid":599255,"uid":54373,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T09:25:55.000Z","msg":"光明正大逃稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hk